item.description:
The Manchester Dog Park Association will be meeting at Piscataquog River Park to discuss the current status of creating the Manchester Dog Park and the remaining issues to be dealt with as well as planning of future events to support our efforts and achieve our goal.

Piscataquog River Park is located at end of Precourt St., off of Varney. There's a fenced ballpark on site, so feel free to bring your dog.

Phil Greazzo
manchdogpark@yahoo.com
item.how_to_find_us: There is a fenced ballpark there, look for people & dogs!
